io.github.zachohara.bukkit.simpleplugin.serializable

Class SerializableLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.Location
      • io.github.zachohara.bukkit.simpleplugin.serializable.SerializableLocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, org.bukkit.configuration.serialization.ConfigurationSerializable

    public class SerializableLocation
extends org.bukkit.Location
implements java.io.Serializable
    A SerializableLocation is a Bukkit Location that can be serialized using Java's standard object IO system.
    Author:
    Zach Ohara
